title: Nawab Malik’s arrest: HC denies interim relief, says debatable issues involved - The Indian Express
content: Nawab Malik’s arrest: HC denies interim relief, says debatable issues involved  The Indian ExpressView Full coverage on Google News
description: The NCP leader had been arrested by the ED for alleged money laundering and “involvement in terror funding” in connection with a 1999 land deal with underworld don Dawood Ibrahim’s sister. Malik had claimed his arrest was "illegal".
